LOCUS       HrU3_ForInd-Extg       11673 bp    DNA     circular SYN 24-MAR-2026
DEFINITION  V5 landing pad-compatible pHrU3 ForInducible vector containing 
            Extended Gag (Humes) with mCherry. Plasmid was generated by 
            digesting p3921 with AscI/MluI and combining with mCherry fragment 
            (amplified from p3137) via HiFi Assembly. Saved Clone 3. Cloned and 
            sequence validated using Primordium whole plasmid sequencing by 
            Arjun Aditham.
